text: Want to cancel Prime membership before renewal date November 18. Already used Prime Video twice this month. Will I get prorated refund?
You can cancel anytime. Since you used Prime Video benefits this month, no prorated refund available. Membership active until November 12.

Two-day shipping unavailable could be seller issue. Prime only applies to Prime-eligible items. I'll help filter for Prime shipping options.

Household sharing for Prime Music requires separate step. I'll enable streaming benefits for added household member in membership settings.
